UK AI ADOPTION (use in conversation):
Barclays Business Prosperity Index (Aug 2025): 89% of UK businesses plan AI use within two years; SMEs (10–49 staff) averaged £125k AI investment vs £400k for 250+ employee firms. Lloyds Business Barometer (Mar 2026): 66% have invested in AI, mostly under £25k—39% cite AI/digital skills shortage. Vet practices use PMS but rarely AI for clinical note scribing or inventory forecasting.

WHERE VA ALONE IS NOT THE RIGHT LEAD:
VA poor for clinical-adjacent PMS tasks—prioritise AI scribing and automated reminders.

SUGGESTED CALL HOOKS / DISCOVERY QUESTIONS:
• Automate vaccination recalls
• AI clinical note drafting
• AI client query triage

